  <brief_title>Optimal Analgesia for Forefoot Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimal Analgesia Following Metatarsal Surgery: A Prospective Randomised, Single-Blind Sham-Controlled Trial of Three Strategies</official_title>
